{% comment %}
  StyleDrop Product Template
  
  Custom product template using all converted React components.
  This template replaces the default Dawn product template with the StyleDrop design.
  
  To use this template:
  1. In Shopify admin, go to Online Store > Themes > Customize
  2. Navigate to a product page
  3. In the left sidebar, under "Template", select "product.styledrop"
  
  Or set as default template for all products by duplicating and renaming to product.liquid
{% endcomment %}

{%- comment -%} Styledrop Product Template (Valgara-style isolated CSS) {%- endcomment -%}
{{ 'styledrop-product.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}
{{ 'styledrop-product-info-panel.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}
{{ 'styledrop-product-add-to-cart.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

{%- comment -%} Product Page Container {%- endcomment -%}
<div class="styledrop-product">
  
  {%- comment -%} 1. Breadcrumb Navigation {%- endcomment -%}
  {% render 'breadcrumb-product' %}

  {%- comment -%} 2. Main Product Section {%- endcomment -%}
  <div class="container styledrop-product__main">
    <div class="styledrop-product__panel">
      
      {%- comment -%} Left Column: Image Gallery {%- endcomment -%}
      <div class="styledrop-product__gallery">
        {% render 'product-image-gallery', product: product %}
      </div>

      {%- comment -%} Right Column: Product Info & Purchase {%- endcomment -%}
      <div class="styledrop-product__info">
        {%- comment -%} Product Info (Title, Brand, Rating, Price) {%- endcomment -%}
        {% render 'product-info-panel', product: product %}

        {%- comment -%} Variant Selector (Color & Size) {%- endcomment -%}
        {% render 'product-variant-selector', product: product %}

        {%- comment -%} Quantity & Add to Cart {%- endcomment -%}
        {% render 'product-add-to-cart', product: product %}

        {%- comment -%} Accordion Sections (Size Guide, Shipping, etc.) {%- endcomment -%}
        {% render 'product-accordion-sections', product: product %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {%- comment -%} 3. Related Products Section {%- endcomment -%}
  {% render 'related-products-section', 
              product: product, 
              collection_handle: 'all' %}

  {%- comment -%} 4. Size Predictor Modal (global, triggered by button) {%- endcomment -%}
  {% render 'size-predictor-modal' %}

</div>

{%- comment -%} Schema for Theme Editor {%- endcomment -%}
{% schema %}
{
  "name": "StyleDrop Product",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "section-styledrop-product",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "StyleDrop Product Template"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "This is a custom product template using the StyleDrop design. All styling is handled by style-drop-custom.css and the component snippets."
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "related_collection",
      "label": "Related Products Collection Handle",
      "default": "all",
      "info": "Enter the handle of the collection to show related products from (e.g. 'featured', 'bestsellers', or leave as 'all')"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}

{% comment %}
  USAGE NOTES:
  
  This template integrates all 8 converted React snippets:
  1. breadcrumb-product.liquid - Navigation breadcrumb
  2. product-image-gallery.liquid - Main image gallery with thumbnails
  3. product-info-panel.liquid - Title, brand, rating, description, price
  4. product-variant-selector.liquid - Color/size selection
  5. product-add-to-cart.liquid - Quantity, add to cart, wishlist
  6. product-accordion-sections.liquid - Collapsible info sections
  7. related-products-section.liquid - "Complete the Look" products
  8. size-predictor-modal.liquid - Smart size calculator modal
  
  FEATURES:
  - ✅ Full StyleDrop design system
  - ✅ Responsive layout (mobile & desktop)
  - ✅ All custom interactions (wishlist, quick add, size predictor)
  - ✅ Shopify native product forms
  - ✅ SEO-friendly structure
  - ✅ No dependencies on Dawn default styles
  
  CUSTOMIZATION:
  - Modify individual snippets for component-level changes
  - Update style-drop-custom.css for design system changes
  - Adjust grid/spacing in this template for layout changes
  
  TESTING CHECKLIST:
  □ Product images load correctly
  □ Variant selection updates price/image
  □ Add to cart adds correct variant
  □ Breadcrumb links work
  □ Related products show recommendations
  □ Size predictor modal opens and calculates
  □ Wishlist button toggles
  □ Mobile responsive layout works
  □ All accordions expand/collapse
{% endcomment %}
